 base management fees and performancebased income as an investor and capital allocator – we strive to invest at attractive valuations particularly in valueoriented situations that create opportunities for superior valuation gains and cash flow returns or by monetizing assets at appropriate times to realize value and as an owneroperator – we constantly work to increase the value of the assets within our operating businesses and the cash flows they produce through our operating expertise development capabilities and effective financing stock quote key links trisura group spinoff tax information q press release q letter to shareholders q  supplemental q  mp recording q  transcript notice and access  brookfield agm webcast notice of annual meeting  management information circular  proxy form – class a shares  annual report  notice and access  brookfield agm webcast notice of annual meeting  management information circular  proxy form – class a shares  annual report  key links trisura group spinoff tax information q press release q letter to shareholders q  supplemental q  mp recording q  transcript brookfield reports  filings view all brookfield events  presentations view all brookfield corporate governance view all brookfield stock  distributions view all latest news brookfield asset management notice of  q results conference call and webcastjuly   brookfield asset management announces results of conversion of its series  preferred sharesjune   brookfield asset management announces say on pay results and election of directorsjune   all press releases shareholder alerts sign up to receive financial information and updates via email register contact brookfield asset management inc linda northwood ir tel    n america tel    international enquiriesbrookfieldcom information request our firm about us global presence leadership corporate social responsibility careers businesses real estate infrastructure renewable power private equity shareholders bam bpy bip bep bbu investor