c riskreturn objectives which may be better suited to separately managed accounts we have a long history of managing separately managed accounts for large institutional investors as well as several different custodians and have deep operational and compliance experience in this regard and maintain advanced oversight systems our portfolio managers collaborate with clients to ensure investment strategies are appropriate for their individual investment objectives  opportunistic strategies in addition to our longonly strategies we have created a number of opportunistic strategies focused on real asset public securities for qualified investors our opportunistic strategies seek to deliver strong absolute returns over a market cycle drawing upon our high conviction approach a valueoriented lens and taking into account the tradeoff between quality and value and a keen awareness for the cyclical nature of capital markets us mutual funds  brookfield global listed infrastructure fund brookfield global listed real estate fund brookfield real assets securities fund brookfield us listed real estate fund ucits brookfield global listed infrastructure longshort ucits fund brookfield global listed infrastructure ucits fund brookfield global listed real estate ucits fund brookfield real assets securities ucits fund brookfield us listed real estate ucits fund us closedend funds brookfield global listed infrastructure income fund brookfield real assets income fund inc canadian closedend funds brookfield global infrastructure securities income fund brookfield select opportunities income fund brookfield new horizons income fund enter fund site brookfield asset management reports  results – brookfield asset management inc skip to main content our firm about us global presence north america europe south america asia pacific leadership corporate social responsibility careers career opportunities businesses real estate sectors leadership shareholders investors corporate social responsibility 